Click on the Edit/Delete link. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/9/9f/Make-a-Slidecast-on-Slideshare-Step-3Bullet2.jpg/v4-460px-Make-a-Slidecast-on-Slideshare-Step-3Bullet2.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/9/9f/Make-a-Slidecast-on-Slideshare-Step-3Bullet2.jpg/v4-760px-Make-a-Slidecast-on-Slideshare-Step-3Bullet2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":570,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
